Before the volleyball tournament, the heights of the players in the volleyball team of city N were measured. It turned out that the height of each volleyball player on this team is greater than 190 cm and less than 210 cm. Choose the statements that are true under the given conditions.

\begin{center}
\begin{tabularx}{\textwidth}{p{0.1cm}X} 
1) & The volleyball team of city N necessarily has a player whose height is 220 cm. \\ 
2) & The volleyball team of city N has no players with a height of 189 cm. \\ 
3) & The height of any volleyball player on this team is less than 210 cm. \\ 
4) & The difference in height between any two players of the volleyball team of city N is more than 20 cm. \\ 
\end{tabularx}
\end{center}

In the answer, write the numbers of the selected statements without spaces, commas, or other additional symbols.

